reviewText: i watched this movie last night, was one of those rare movies that was so bad it was good. i kept watching just to see what stupid thing they would do next. all in all i actually ended up enjoying the movie. don't go into it with any high expectations. empty your mind and just watch. the women were not that great looking, no t@a. and the movie ended just as i figured from near the beginning.
I don't review movies past the star rating system
the movie was great and had a lot of action too.
